ygData.msgSnippet: Pull your head out of your ass and pay attention where you re spamming.  I ve been a witch for years, but I can still keep my real-life magic(k) lists separate
ygData.messageBody:
Pull your head out of your ass and pay attention where you're
spamming. I've been a witch for years, but I can still keep my
real-life magic(k) lists separate from the fantasy lists! A good
portion of the discipline is PAYING ATTENTION. Doesn't say much for
your methods or your list, I'm afraid.

On Tue, 06 Jun 2000 14:55:24 -0000, you wrote:

:I believe in the power of the mind.
:I want people to share the results that they have achieved using
:thought control, affirmations and the pure power of their minds. Does
:belief really work ? If you know that it does, share your experiences.
:I want to learn. I want to hear about techniques that work. I want to
:hear of the results that people have achieved using the pure power
:of their minds.
:Please join www.egroups.com/group/MindPowerResults
